{"word":"H6658 - צָדָה - tsâdâh - tsaw-daw' - Destroy","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָדָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tsâdâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-daw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Destroy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பதிவிரு, வேட்டையாடு, அவாந்தரையாகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) (Qal) to lie in wait"},{"paragraph":"2) to lay waste; (Niphal) to be laid waste"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>chase</i>; by implication to <i>desolate: - </i>destroy, hunt, lie in wait."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6658 - צָדָה - tsâdâh - tsaw-daw'/6658\">H6658</a>, <a href=\"#/H6660 - צְדִיָּה - tsᵉdîyâh - tsed-ee-yaw'/6660\">H6660</a>"}]}